::Skulletron::

	Now, the intruder was caught, and with his mind ability, there would
hopefully be one less pred and one more relationship!!!!!!!!!!!

	Skulletron decided to go get some fresh air, so he headed towards the
entrance.  On the way, he saw Chordate, Feline and Gigatron.

	"Ah, we meet again," He said to Chordate, "You remember me, don't you?  Oh
ya, we have taken care of that intruder," He looked at Feline with a grin.

	"Oh hello there.  My name is Skulletron, and who might you be?" He said to
Feline, trying to make it seem as if he had never met her.
